{"tid":1606870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"潑漆案警界高層生氣了！　祭出鐵腕裁定：不准統促黨借北車辦活動","createTime":"2019-09-30T16:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T16:44:54.000Z","uid":322955,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"eaef8718d2d04fd8c0e00ef01bf9fc8a72d4e921","tid":1606870,"uid":322955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:18:35.000Z","msg":"潑漆案警界高層生氣了！　祭出鐵腕裁定：不准統促黨借北車辦活動   <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於統促黨成員29日策畫潑漆惡搞香港反送中藝人何韻詩，傾中政黨人員突襲成功造成台北市警局顏面無光、背負維安不力的龐大輿論壓力；台北市警局、市刑大與刑事局緊急成立專案小組、2天內逮捕9名傾中團體大陳島鄉情文化促進會成員，今晚9點更宣布中華統一促進黨「慶祝光輝十月廟會民俗活動」集會活動申請許可不通過！<br />\n警界高層生氣了！台北市警局今晚9時許宣布：中華統一促進黨向台北市中正一警分局申請10月10於臺北車站南2門前廣場舉辦「慶祝光輝十月廟會民俗活動」警方考量台北車站處於三鐵共構之交通樞紐，旅客往來眾多，為保障大眾交通秩序及公共利益，不許可該團體於該處舉行集會。<br />\n台北市警局保安科說明：鑒於9月29日發生統促黨黨部主委等人涉嫌潑漆施暴案，內政部警政署陳家欽署長於30日召集臺北市政府警察局及刑事警察局等相關單位召開專案會議，再次嚴厲譴責暴力犯罪行為，並指示北市警方嚴正執法。<br />\n市警局表示：由於該政黨團體舉辦活動發生暴力鬥毆、暴力攻擊他人的情況屢見不顯，為保障大眾交通秩序，經專業評估後，不准許統促黨當天於北車舉行該活動，也請外界勿作過多政治聯想。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190930/1546655.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190930%2F1546655.htm&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6pMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=8f2c5042\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190930/1546655.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n潑漆完<br />\n台灣警政署直接把統促黨活動直接取消了<br />\n代理人法本來這個會期沒有要討論的<br />\n現在變成優先法案&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n嗯&hellip;大外宣團體bye bye"},{"pid":"8a0c3f3ee29fc6ad70230b1ac44d6e28430548d8","tid":1606870,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:20:34.000Z","msg":"統佢地老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58a469c3d8a4b3902f09b099f077dad23331e8c","tid":1606870,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:20:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a94472760be9f3e7c110bf45a4b04aedd4ff60","tid":1606870,"uid":196745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:21:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ec7fea8d9082534b2c2617976824923620f007","tid":1606870,"uid":129466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:22:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />奶共下場"},{"pid":"9c9f2fc8d615d12579c611de27e77e232830dcc5","tid":1606870,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a0ab0fb7e246b29f3f676eae725cc44ac7d58d","tid":1606870,"uid":59839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:23:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/china999/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fchina999%2F&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6pMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=a20e2c1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/china999/</a>"},{"pid":"f4093231728845df8e6276d3df2cc52b3474dc42","tid":1606870,"uid":39277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:27:07.000Z","msg":"人地啲警察<br />\n潑漆依啲小事（經過依三個月，覺得好少事）<br />\n都嚴正處理<br />\n<br />\n我地啲警察<br />\n721恐襲就唔見人，同啲黑社會搭晒膊頭<br />\n831就製造恐襲"},{"pid":"ae93c0bedd62eb64bf500f84fb883c896bf3e4fc","tid":1606870,"uid":179649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:31:55.000Z","msg":"係台灣慶祝支那 on99<br />\n判班仆街叛國罪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係掉哂番大陸"},{"pid":"0044d77ba121b279746d9b4810ccd4084cf49ecd","tid":1606870,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:44:54.000Z","msg":"比人借啲意收皮<br />\n只怪自己on9"}]}